race.comment: PATTERA (3) showed good early dash and raced on the speed last start before fading to finish fourth over 1300m at Dubbo. Will race handy and take running down. GEOSTORM (5) disappointed last start when out of the placings over 1400m at Sapphire Coast. Back in class and the claim helps his cause. MORE VOLTAGE (7) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start when fifth over 1200m at this track. Finds the right race this time and can get the job done. INDIVIDUALIST (12) was right in the market last start in a similar race at Dubbo, though he was a touch disappointing there. Gets Lisnyy in the saddle today however and he can bounce back to form.
